UI.Controls.RichEdit.json

# Shell, input, accessibility (typical GUI apps)
UI.Shell.json
UI.Shell.Common.json
UI.Shell.PropertiesSystem.json
UI.Input.json
UI.Input.KeyboardAndMouse.json
UI.Accessibility.json
UI.HiDpi.json

